projects.title: John Walter Concept
projects.contentSummary: Discover how we gave this startup a fresh visual start. With over 50 team members, 5000+ users and 27M, it was time to replace their outdated look with a design that matched their ambitions. Webflow is the Berlin-based Series A startup on its way to becoming the leading finance platform for SMEs, freelancers, and self-employed persons.
